text: William Wiseman may refer to: *Sir William Wiseman, 1st Baronet (1629–1688), English landowner and politician *Sir William Wiseman, 8th Baronet (1814–1874), British naval officer *Sir William Wiseman, 10th Baronet (1885–1962), grandson of the above, head of Secret Intelligence Service in Washington, DC during the First World War *William Wiseman (sheriff of Elgin), 13th–14th century Scottish nobleman and the Sheriff of Elgin *Willie Wiseman (1896–1979), Scottish footballer (Queen's Park and Scotland) ==See also== *Wiseman baronets
title: William Wiseman
